Class Summary
DefaultFMatrixConfiguration Defaultimplementation of the IFMatrixConfiguration interface.
FMatrixContext  
FMatrixManager controller class for the x- and y-Dimension of the fmatrix and the bit matrix.
FMatrixService  
FMatrixTaskPart  
LineInformation holds all line information per file.
Match represents a point of the fmatrix.
SourceInformation Class stores all processed information of the used source files (dotplot sourcefiles) for later retrieval.
TokenInformation Stores additional token information, such as Filedetails, row info., etc.
TokenTable a TokenTable object holds all tokens(rather their index) of one axis(dimension) of the dotplot.
TokenType this entity is used to store, modify and access a tokentype and all needed information of this type for the fmatrix.
TypeTable This class is used as a datastorage for token types in the sense of the fMatrix.
TypeTableManipulator The class holds several functions to maniplate the typeTable.
TypeTableNavigator an object of this class allows to navigate through tokentypes and all neccessary information.
WeightingEntry Class to store the manual weightings wich will later be stored in the GlobalConfiguration.
